{"id":867,"parent_id":828,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":867,"title":"Ezekiel 39","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ezek.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 39"],[".studySummary",["i","Gog and the land of Magog will be destroyed—For seven years the people in the cities of Israel will burn the weapons of war—For seven months they will bury the dead—Then will come the supper of the great God and the continued gathering of Israel."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.1","order":"02.27.039.57991"},["b","1"],"Therefore, thou son of man, prophesy against",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Gog"],", and say, Thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Behold, I",["i","am"],"against thee, O Gog, the chief prince of Meshech and Tubal:"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.2","order":"02.27.039.57992"},["b","2"],"And I will turn thee back, and leave but the sixth part of thee, and will cause thee to come up from the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"north"],"parts, and will bring thee upon the mountains of Israel:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.3","order":"02.27.039.57993"},["b","3"],"And I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"smite"],"thy bow out of thy left hand, and will cause thine arrows to fall out of thy right hand."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.4","order":"02.27.039.57994"},["b","4"],"Thou shalt fall upon the mountains of Israel, thou, and all thy bands, and the people that",["i","is"],"with thee: I will give thee unto the ravenous birds of every sort, and",["i","to"],"the beasts of the field to be devoured."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.5","order":"02.27.039.57995"},["b","5"],"Thou shalt fall upon the open field: for I have spoken",["i","it,"],"saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.6","order":"02.27.039.57996"},["b","6"],"And I will send a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"fire"],"on Magog, and among them that dwell",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"carelessly"],"in the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"isles"],": and they shall know that I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.7","order":"02.27.039.57997"},["b","7"],"So will I make my holy name",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"known"],"in the midst of my people Israel; and I will not",["i","let them"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"pollute"],"my holy name any more: and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"heathen"],"shall",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_7d"},"know"],"that I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", the Holy One in Israel."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.8","order":"02.27.039.57998"},["b","8"],"¶Behold, it is come, and it is done, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; this",["i","is"],"the day whereof I have spoken."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.9","order":"02.27.039.57999"},["b","9"],"And they that dwell in the cities of Israel shall go forth, and shall set on fire and burn the weapons, both the shields and the bucklers, the bows and the arrows, and the handstaves, and the spears, and they shall burn them with fire seven years:"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.10","order":"02.27.039.58000"},["b","10"],"So that they shall take no wood out of the field, neither cut down",["i","any"],"out of the forests; for they shall burn the weapons with fire: and they shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"spoil"],"those that spoiled them, and rob those that robbed them, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.11","order":"02.27.039.58001"},["b","11"],"¶And it shall come to pass in that day,",["i","that"],"I will give unto Gog a place there of graves in Israel, the valley of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"passengers"],"on the east of the sea: and it shall stop the",["i","noses"],"of the passengers: and there shall they bury Gog and all his multitude: and they shall call",["i","it"],"The valley of Hamon-gog."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.12","order":"02.27.039.58002"},["b","12"],"And seven months shall the house of Israel be burying of them, that they may cleanse the land."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.13","order":"02.27.039.58003"},["b","13"],"Yea, all the people of the land shall bury",["i","them;"],"and it shall be to them",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"a renown"],"the day that I shall be glorified, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.14","order":"02.27.039.58004"},["b","14"],"And they shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"sever out"],"men of continual employment, passing through the land to bury with the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"passengers"],"those that remain upon the face of the earth, to cleanse it: after the end of seven months shall they search."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.15","order":"02.27.039.58005"},["b","15"],"And the passengers",["i","that"],"pass through the land, when",["i","any"],"seeth a man’s bone, then shall he set up a sign by it, till the buriers have buried it in the valley of Hamon-gog."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.16","order":"02.27.039.58006"},["b","16"],"And also the name of the city",["i","shall be"],"Hamonah. Thus shall they cleanse the land."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.17","order":"02.27.039.58007"},["b","17"],"¶And, thou son of man, thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Speak unto every feathered fowl, and to every",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"beast"],"of the field, Assemble yourselves, and come; gather yourselves on every side to my sacrifice that I do sacrifice for you,",["i","even"],"a great sacrifice upon the mountains of Israel, that ye may eat flesh, and drink blood."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.18","order":"02.27.039.58008"},["b","18"],"Ye shall eat the flesh of the mighty, and drink the blood of the princes of the earth, of rams, of lambs, and of goats, of bullocks, all of them fatlings of Bashan."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.19","order":"02.27.039.58009"},["b","19"],"And ye shall eat fat till ye be full, and drink blood till ye be drunken, of my sacrifice which I have sacrificed for you."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.20","order":"02.27.039.58010"},["b","20"],"Thus ye shall be filled at my table with horses and chariots, with mighty men, and with all men of war, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.21","order":"02.27.039.58011"},["b","21"],"And I will set my glory among the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"heathen"],", and all the heathen shall see my judgment that I have executed, and my hand that I have laid upon them."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.22","order":"02.27.039.58012"},["b","22"],"So the house of Israel shall know that I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"their God from that day and forward."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.23","order":"02.27.039.58013"},["b","23"],"¶And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"heathen"],"shall know that the house of Israel went into captivity for their iniquity: because they trespassed against me, therefore",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"hid"],"I my face from them, and gave them into the hand of their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_23c"},"enemies"],": so fell they all by the sword."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.24","order":"02.27.039.58014"},["b","24"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"According"],"to their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"uncleanness"],"and according to their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_24c"},"transgressions"],"have I done unto them, and hid my face from them."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.25","order":"02.27.039.58015"},["b","25"],"Therefore thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Now will I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"bring"],"again the captivity of Jacob, and have mercy upon the whole house of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"Israel"],", and will be jealous for my holy name;"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.26","order":"02.27.039.58016"},["b","26"],"After that they have borne their shame, and all their trespasses whereby they have trespassed against me, when they dwelt safely in their land, and none made",["i","them"],"afraid."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.27","order":"02.27.039.58017"},["b","27"],"When I have brought them again from the people, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"gathered"],"them out of their enemies’ lands, and am sanctified in them in the sight of many nations;"],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.28","order":"02.27.039.58018"},["b","28"],"Then shall they know that I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"their God, which caused them to be led into captivity among the heathen: but I have gathered them unto their own land, and have left none of them any more there."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.29","order":"02.27.039.58019"},["b","29"],"Neither will I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"hide"],"my face any more from them: for I have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_29b"},"poured"],"out my spirit upon the house of Israel, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.1a","order":"02.27.039.58020"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/38.2.2-3"},"Ezek. 38:2 (2–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.2a","order":"02.27.039.58022"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/38.15"},"Ezek. 38:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.3a","order":"02.27.039.58024"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.20"},"Joel 2:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/12.9"},"Zech. 12:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.6a","order":"02.27.039.58026"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/38.22"},"Ezek. 38:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.6b","order":"02.27.039.58028"},["b","6b"],["span.small","HEB"],"securely, confidently, without care."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.6c","order":"02.27.039.58030"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/26.15"},"Ezek. 26:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/27.15.3,6-7,15"},"27:15 (3, 6–7, 15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/10.20"},"2 Ne. 10:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.7a","order":"02.27.039.58032"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-knowledge-about"},"TG God, Knowledge about"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.7b","order":"02.27.039.58034"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/20.39"},"Ezek. 20:39"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/43.7"},"43:7"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/pollution"},"TG Pollution"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.7c","order":"02.27.039.58036"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conversion"},"TG Conversion"],"."],["div",{"id":"7d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.7d","order":"02.27.039.58038"},["b","7d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/38.23"},"Ezek. 38:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.10a","order":"02.27.039.58040"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/14.2"},"Isa. 14:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.11a","order":"02.27.039.58042"},["b","11a"],["span.small","HEB"],"travelers."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.13a","order":"02.27.039.58044"},["b","13a"],["span.small","HEB"],"a name; i.e., famous."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.14a","order":"02.27.039.58046"},["b","14a"],["span.small","HEB"],"separate, set apart."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.14b","order":"02.27.039.58048"},["b","14b"],["span.small","HEB"],"travelers."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.17a","order":"02.27.039.58050"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.20.17-20"},"D&C 29:20 (17–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.21a","order":"02.27.039.58052"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conversion"},"TG Conversion"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heathen"},"Heathen"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.23a","order":"02.27.039.58054"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conversion"},"TG Conversion"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.23b","order":"02.27.039.58056"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/31.17.16-17"},"Deut. 31:17 (16–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"23c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.23c","order":"02.27.039.58058"},["b","23c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/26.25"},"Lev. 26:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.24a","order":"02.27.039.58060"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/36.19"},"Ezek. 36:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.24b","order":"02.27.039.58062"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/uncleanness"},"TG Uncleanness"],"."],["div",{"id":"24c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.24c","order":"02.27.039.58064"},["b","24c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/transgress"},"TG Transgress"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.25a","order":"02.27.039.58066"},["b","25a"],["span.small","HEB"],"restore Jacob from exile."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.25b","order":"02.27.039.58068"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-twelve-tribes-of"},"TG Israel, Twelve Tribes of"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.27a","order":"02.27.039.58070"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-gathering-of"},"TG Israel, Gathering of"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.29a","order":"02.27.039.58072"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/54.8"},"Isa. 54:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"29b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.29b","order":"02.27.039.58074"},["b","29b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/12.10"},"Zech. 12:10"],"."]]}
